{"tid":1694071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗話根源是暴力：「停止咗落嚟，警方唔洗回應，大家幾好呢」","createTime":"2019-11-05T02:51:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T06:02:46.000Z","uid":57012,"like":114,"dislike":319,"uniUserReply":131,"replies":[{"pid":"b4147988cc56f9e82b26b09bcfaaf0f5114e2c4c","tid":1694071,"uid":57012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:51:59.000Z","msg":"報導：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/36zpcVC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F36zpcVC&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwOoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=0562fd11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/36zpcVC</a><br />\n<br />\n署理行政長官、政務司司長張建宗認為，警員與記者就採訪上的問題根源是示威者的「暴力」，「暴力停止咗落嚟，警方唔洗回應，大家幾好呢，記者又唔洗咁辛苦，可以做正經&hellip;&hellip;正常好既新聞，就唔洗寫一啲咁樣&hellip;&hellip;啲新聞亦跑得好辛苦，大家都。」<br />\n<br />\n有記者續追問指警員針對記者已成常態，是否應有系統性調查解決。張建宗則指，警隊設有傳媒聯絡隊，在現場擔任中間聯絡人，「我相信呢啲係人同人既工程，一定可以透過大家既關係和態度既改變，能夠紓緩個氣氛。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無惡法，點會有示威出現<br />\n無警暴，點會有暴力反抗</span></span>"},{"pid":"d1107086a46c747408ed72419e69403f00491650","tid":1694071,"uid":293667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:52:31.000Z","msg":"制裁TVB聯署 尚欠51,000人聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1693299\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1693299</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bad2c85cdb9e4b2ee612c9e3d3c09262847e3fc9","tid":1694071,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:53:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b62867d0abd85bc575c44510692743110c049a3","tid":1694071,"uid":57012,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:53:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Obvk40Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FObvk40Y.png&h=ec63afc1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"412b7e0b0787d6533a7062c00468c9b401577ecb","tid":1694071,"uid":41974,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"ci